channel.title: New command that automatically puts the items you want on your guy
channel.description:
Allright if any of you have ever played FrugooScape I've figured out how to make one of his commands The new command I've made automatically changes your characters armor to the armor\weapon you want in your set. Vote if you want me to release. :)
Note: once I get 20 yes votes I will release and create some sort of tutorial
